<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4c.48.22-23_0001a" />

<opener>

<note>Skyrim Farm
4-28-'66</note>

<dateline>April 28, 6'6</dateline>


<salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
</opener>
<p>I have been reading <hi rend="underline">"I Fought with Geronimo"</hi> ever since it arrived, and I have greatly enjoyed it. Also, I prize the inscriptions on the flyleaf. What a man that was!! <hi rend="underline">Is</hi> he still living? I was especially glad to have this Apache's estimate

<pb facs="nei.j4c.48.22-23_0001b"/>
<fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
<fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>

of General Crook, who is a big figure in the history of my Plains Indians.</p>

<p><hi rend="underline">Many thanks</hi>!!</p>

<p>I'm about to begin (May 4th) a rather strenuous period of lecturing, ending July 8th. I do hope my eyes will carry me through. I think they will, with the aid of my illuminated reading glass.</p>

<fw type="curatorial">22</fw>
<pb facs="nei.j4c.48.22-23_0002"/>
<fw type="authorial">-3-</fw>

<closer>
<salute>With the old affection &#8212;</salute>
<signed>John N</signed>
</closer>

</div1>
</body>

